{
    "body": "<p>Dhampirs are defined by class levels&mdash;they don't possess racial Hit Dice. All dhampirs have the following racial traits.</p>", 
    "name": "Dhampir", 
    "source": "Bestiary 2", 
    "url": "pfsrd://Bestiary 2/Monsters/Dhampir/Dhampir", 
    "type": "race", 
    "section_id": 597, 
    "subtype": "monster_race", 
    "sections": [
        {
            "body": "<p>Dhampirs are fast and seductive, but closer to death than most mortals.</p>", 
            "source": "Bestiary 2", 
            "type": "section", 
            "name": "+2 Dexterity, +2 Charisma, -2 Constitution", 
            "section_id": 598
        }, 
        {
            "body": "<p>Low-light vision and darkvision 60 feet.</p>", 
            "name": "Senses", 
            "url": "pfsrd://Bestiary 2/Monsters/Dhampir/Dhampir/Senses", 
            "section_id": 599, 
            "source": "Bestiary 2", 
            "type": "section"
        }, 
        {
            "body": "<p>+2 racial bonus on Bluff and Perception.</p>", 
            "name": "Manipulative", 
            "url": "pfsrd://Bestiary 2/Monsters/Dhampir/Dhampir/Manipulative", 
            "section_id": 600, 
            "source": "Bestiary 2", 
            "type": "section"
        }, 
        {
            "body": "<p>Dhampirs gain a +2 racial bonus on saving throws against disease and mind-affecting effects.</p>", 
            "name": "Undead Resistance", 
            "url": "pfsrd://Bestiary 2/Monsters/Dhampir/Dhampir/Undead Resistance", 
            "section_id": 601, 
            "source": "Bestiary 2", 
            "type": "section"
        }, 
        {
            "body": "See Universal Monster Rules/Light Sensitivity</p>", 
            "source": "Bestiary 2", 
            "type": "link", 
            "name": "Light Sensitivity", 
            "section_id": 602
        }, 
        {
