            "type": "link", 
            "name": "Negative Energy Affinity", 
            "section_id": 603
        }, 
        {
            "body": "<p>A dhampir can use<i> detect undead</i> three times per day as a spell-like ability. The caster level for this ability equals the dhampir's class level.</p>", 
            "name": "Spell-Like Ability", 
            "url": "pfsrd://Bestiary 2/Monsters/Dhampir/Dhampir/Spell-Like Ability", 
